@startuml seq_password_reset
!theme plain
title Sequence Diagram: Password Reset Flow

skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "User" as User
participant "React SPA" as Client
participant "Kong API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Auth Service" as Auth
database "Redis (Cache)" as Redis
participant "SMTP Server" as Email
database "PostgreSQL (HA)" as PG

== 1. Request OTP for Password Reset ==
User -> Client : Input Email & Click "Forgot Password"
Client -> Gateway : POST /api/otp/send-otp
Gateway -> Auth : Route Request
Auth -> Redis : SET otp:<email> with TTL (5 minutes)
Auth -> Email : Send OTP via Nodemailer
Email -> User : Deliver Email
Auth -> Client : 200 OK (OTP Sent)

== 2. Verify OTP & Reset Password ==
User -> Client : Input OTP & New Password
Client -> Gateway : POST /api/otp/reset-password
Gateway -> Auth : Route Request

Auth -> Redis : GET otp:<email>
Redis --> Auth : Return Stored OTP

alt OTP matches
    Auth -> Auth : Bcrypt.hash(newPassword)
    Auth -> PG : UPDATE users SET password = hashed_password WHERE email = :email
    Auth -> Redis : DEL otp:<email> (Invalidate OTP)
    Auth -> Client : 200 OK (Password Reset Successfully)
end
@enduml